headline: Humana Foundation Donates $250,000 to Support Disaster Recovery in the Wake of Catastrophic Flooding in Kentucky
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., February 24, 2025--The Humana Foundation, the philanthropic arm of Humana Inc. (NYSE: HUM), is donating $250,000 in support of relief and recovery efforts for Kentuckians impacted by destructive flooding in Eastern Kentucky. Following the flooding, some areas were also hit by winter snowstorm activity.
